title: Font Collection (65,000+ fonts)
description:
This is a compilation of fonts that I downloaded here at PirateBay.org.  I take no credit for being the first to post these.  I simply cleaned up the collection a bit.

The cleanup involved using FontExpert to locate corrupt and duplicate fonts, deleting these fonts, and sorting everything else into alphabetical folders.

This is my first attempt at uploading a torrent, so please take it easy on me :)

Enjoy.
